{
  "texts": [
    "Transformers, coupled with breakthrough language models, have played a crucial role in the widespread adoption of generative AI.",
    "These models, with billions or trillions of parameters, have the capacity to write engaging text, create realistic images, and even generate entertaining sitcoms.",
    "Multimodal AI innovations further extend generative AI's capabilities, enabling content creation across various media types, including text, graphics, and video.",
    "Despite the progress, early implementations of generative AI faced challenges such as accuracy issues, biases, hallucinations, and odd responses.",
    "Nevertheless, the technology's potential to transform enterprise operations is significant, with envisioned applications ranging from code writing and drug design to product development and supply chain transformation."
  ]
}